~ Installing Visual Studio Code
  ~ Installing extension called Prettier
  ~ Inside the Visual Studio Code Setting, search for default formatter and change it to Prettier.
    ~ Search for Format On Save, and checklist => will format when you save it
    ~ Search for Auto Save and change it to onFocusChange => will save your work, when you move from your
      current window or editor.
    ~ Search for Tab Size, and change it to 2.